1
00:00:41,679 --> 00:00:44,039
You're interested in Plot 73 too

2
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:46,600
I'm interested in the new Development zone

3
00:00:46,759 --> 00:00:48,359
It's good for young people to have guts

4
00:00:49,399 --> 00:00:51,000
But it depends on who you're up against

5
00:00:53,079 --> 00:00:54,679
In business, winner takes all

6
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:57,079
It's all about financial strength

7
00:00:59,159 --> 00:01:00,479
Then let's wait and see

8
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,799
Plot 73

9
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:11,200
Prosperity Group must win it

10
00:01:17,239 --> 00:01:18,719
The live bidding is already at 8 billion

11
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:20,000
Young Master Sheng is awaiting your orders

12
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,799
Who placed the bid?

13
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:22,439
The Long family, Zhang Xiaobei

14
00:01:22,439 --> 00:01:23,079
Match it

15
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:23,840
Yes

16
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:31,359
Father, it's already up to 10 billion

17
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:33,560
Match it

18
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,200
Okay, Father

19
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,840
Wait, don't hang up

20
00:01:39,159 --> 00:01:40,879
I want updates immediately

21
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,920
11 billion

22
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,200
11.5 billion

23
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,079
12 billion

24
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:49,439
Father

25
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,159
This price far exceeds

26
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:52,120
its profit value

27
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,200
I want Plot 73

28
00:01:57,920 --> 00:02:00,239
Chairman Sheng, congrats on becoming the new land king

29
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,359
What?

30
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,360
A financial group from Singapore

31
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,719
decided to invest 20 billion in the West District

32
00:02:10,719 --> 00:02:12,960
to build a top-tier deep-water port in the country

33
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:14,280
If the deep-water port

34
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:16,199
is built in the West District

35
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:18,639
then the East District's chances of being the Development zone

36
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:19,800
will be very small

37
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:20,960
What about the West District?

38
00:02:21,319 --> 00:02:22,240
Did anyone buy it?

39
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:23,599
This afternoon

40
00:02:23,919 --> 00:02:25,800
Plot 32 in the West District

41
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,680
was sold for 6.2 billion

42
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,680
Who bought it?

43
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,919
All we know is he's a rich businessman from Shanxi

44
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,280
After weighing multiple factors

45
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,400
we've decided

46
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,400
in Jinghai City's West District

47
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,599
to establish a new Development zone

48
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,960
and focus on developing it

49
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:42,360
around the West deep-water port

50
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,719
into a Port City

51
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,199
They think

52
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,759
our 12 billion cost basis is too high

53
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:54,759
the market generally lacks confidence in our profitability

54
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:56,000
and development will be hard to push forward

55
00:02:58,919 --> 00:03:00,719
Prosperity Group shares

56
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:02,199
Buy as much as you can

57
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,400
Someone's buying up large amounts of

58
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,719
Prosperity Group shares

59
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,560
but we don't know who it is yet

60
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:10,479
Sheng Yuanzhou. He must be behind this

61
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,280
I'm gonna kill him

62
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:15,240
Zhang Xiaobei

63
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,360
Explain this to me

64
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,639
Where did you get it?

65
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,639
Someone mailed it to the Newspaper office where I work

66
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,159
Spit it out!

67
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,960
Did you poison Master Long?

68
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,280
How could I?

69
00:03:39,759 --> 00:03:40,680
Master Long

70
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,960
You're cured of the poison?

71
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:47,159
I was never poisoned

72
00:03:51,599 --> 00:03:52,479
I checked it

73
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:53,240
Only the surface was laced with poison

74
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:55,759
They're trying to use you to get rid of me

75
00:03:55,759 --> 00:03:57,960
and then pin it on you

76
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,719
Perfect, then

77
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:02,560
We'll beat them at their own game

78
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:10,960
This is a fake Long Family Inkstone

79
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,439
and the Baochi Motors files

80
00:04:12,639 --> 00:04:13,759
I'm counting on you for everything

81
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:14,800
Don't worry

82
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:20,680
I've never misjudged anyone

83
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,680
Sorry

84
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:22,959
For making you worry

85
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:25,160
To fool that old fox Sheng Shizhong

86
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:27,040
we have to fool everyone

87
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:28,040
I get it

88
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:30,040
Hot, hot, hot!

89
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,439
Coming through, coming through! Make way!

90
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,800
Lisa

91
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:35,360
Big Sis Si Qi, you're here

92
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,120
So that day

93
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,600
you were putting on an act too

94
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:43,040
Otherwise

95
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:45,600
how could we get Sheng Shizhong to spare no expense?

96
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:48,240
This Malatang place is really good

97
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,480
Big Sis Si Qi, here

98
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:50,399
Chopsticks

99
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,000
I won't join you

100
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,079
I have things to do

101
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,160
You guys go ahead

102
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,160
Go on back

103
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,120
Ride safe, okay?

104
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,040
Don't worry

105
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,879
I've gotten the hang of it now

106
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,040
I'm off

107
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:27,000
I really underestimated him

108
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,639
He actually picked up a lot of skills from the Long family

109
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:31,800
The public announcement is out

110
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,759
HA Capital has already acquired

111
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:35,560
over five percent of Prosperity Group's shares

112
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,560
From what I know

113
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,959
it's the same person who bought the plot in the West District

114
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,720
Looks like they're coming for me

115
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,480
Go look into it

116
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:46,240
You must find this person

117
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,439
No matter what it takes

118
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,240
I want to meet him myself

119
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,360
I found him

120
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:52,439
He really likes fishing

121
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:54,279
He often goes to Yingzhou Fishing Ground

122
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,720
Yingzhou Fishing Ground

123
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:17,120
It's you

124
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,040
Long time no see

125
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:34,920
No way

126
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:36,879
You're just a driver

127
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:38,160
How could you have that much money?

128
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,000
Where there's a will, there's a way

129
00:06:40,439 --> 00:06:43,560
After all, I'm the real Sheng Shizhong

130
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:44,600
Bullshit!

131
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:47,079
I'm the real Sheng Shizhong

132
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,079
I am!

133
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,720
It doesn't matter anymore

134
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,360
Bai Zimei is gone

135
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:54,399
Whether I'm Sheng Shizhong or not

136
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:55,959
means nothing to me

137
00:06:59,399 --> 00:07:01,079
Right now, for me

138
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,160
the only thing that matters

139
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:05,759
is making sure you're left with nothing again

140
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,600
to avenge Zimei

141
00:07:08,279 --> 00:07:09,000
Impossible

142
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,279
How could you do that?

143
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,000
I won't let you make a comeback

144
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,480
I won't let you!

145
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:30,240
So, how was I? Did I look convincing?

146
00:07:30,519 --> 00:07:31,600
Judging by his reaction,

147
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,120
he definitely bought it.

148
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,360
It's time to close the net.

149
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,720
It's not this guy.

150
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,000
His name is Hu Jin.

151
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,600
Hu Jin.

152
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:56,240
Hu Jin.

153
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:20,040
How could he know he's Sheng Shizhong?

154
00:08:20,959 --> 00:08:22,959
Did he use my Key of Fate?

155
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:24,720
No way.

156
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:27,360
He doesn't even know the Key of Fate exists.

157
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:28,879
Impossible.

158
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,519
Unless...

159
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:44,159
Zhang Xiaobei.

160
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,360
Welcome.

161
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:02,120
What room are those two from earlier in?

162
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:03,080
I'm sorry.

163
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,919
We can't share other guests' information.

164
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,360
You don't recognize me?

165
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,600
Sorry, Mr. Sheng.

166
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:12,720
Those two from earlier are in Room 608.

167
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:19,360
Fa...

168
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:19,919
Where are they?

169
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:20,519
Father.

170
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:21,480
Get out here!

171
00:09:25,639 --> 00:09:26,600
Father, let me explain!

172
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,320
Get the hell away from me!
